\"is-layout-flow wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffffff;font-size:18px\">GoTriple Ambassadors are social sciences and humanities researchers and engineers with open science at heart.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffffff;font-size:18px\"> Together, we are building a unique network of stakeholders committed to making open research practices and SSH research outputs accessible to all. <\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull is-light\" style=\"min-height:394px\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"has-white-background-color has-background-dim-40 wp-block-cover__gradient-background has-background-dim\"><\/span><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\">\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center has-white-background-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"color:#625e5e\"><strong>What do GoTriple Ambassadors do ? <\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flex wp-container-6 wp-block-columns alignwide\">\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-column has-text-color\" style=\"color:#625e5e\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-x-large-font-size\">\ud83e\udd1d <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:18px\">They <strong>connect<\/strong> with the community and <strong>advocate<\/strong> for <strong>open research practices<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-column has-text-color\" style=\"color:#625e5e\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-x-large-font-size\">\ud83d\udd0e<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:18px\">They help users <strong>discover<\/strong> the advantages of using the GoTriple platform for research and <strong>collaboration<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-column has-text-color\" style=\"color:#625e5e\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-x-large-font-size\">\ud83d\udde3<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:18px\">They share their <strong>feedback<\/strong> on the unique features of <strong>GoTriple<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull is-light\" style=\"min-height:20em\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"has-white-background-color has-background-dim-40 wp-block-cover__gradient-background has-background-dim\"><\/span><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\">\n<div class=\"is-layout-flex wp-container-9 wp-block-columns alignwide\">\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-column has-text-color\" style=\"color:#625e5e\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-stevehenty-drop-shadow-box dropshadowboxes-container\" style=\"width:auto\"><div class=\"dropshadowboxes-drop-shadow dropshadowboxes-lifted-both dropshadowboxes-rounded-corners dropshadowboxes-inside-and-outside-shadow\" style=\"background-color:#fcb900;border-style:solid;border-width:0;border-color:#DDDDDD;width:;padding:50px\"><div>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Are you enthusiastic about sharing scientific knowledge, connecting with peers and building a community around shared values? <\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-horizontal is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-7 wp-block-buttons\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-width wp-block-button__width-50 has-custom-font-size is-style-fill has-medium-font-size\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-text-color\" style=\"border-radius:37px;color:#e1e1e1\"><strong>Join the GoTriple Ambassador Community<\/strong><\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull is-light has-custom-content-position is-position-center-right\" style=\"min-height:1015px\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"has-white-b